{"tid":2001811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察招募日前港隊應徵「因機場特警制服有型」","createTime":"2020-05-04T21:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T08:12:15.000Z","uid":297241,"like":2,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9c79fb6b66767a88da5aa37d29b3f316706f5263","tid":2001811,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T21:33:30.000Z","msg":"警察招募日　考生想做一姐<br />\n前港隊應徵「因機場特警制服有型」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警察總部昨舉行春季警察招募日，收到逾2,000份申請，當中見習督察競爭最激烈，約40人爭1個位。有投考見習督察應徵者豪言「想做一姐」，<span style=\"color: red;\">被問《逃犯條例》修訂等，則拒絕評論</span>。港隊田徑隊前成員盧嘉琳亦<span style=\"color: red;\">投考見習督察，指對機場特警最有興趣，因「套深藍色制服特別有型」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方指今次招募日收到2,010份申請，以警員最多，有1,113份；800人申請見習督察職位，另有97人申請做輔警。招募組署理警司胡志恆指，申請數字與以往相若，不過競爭仍激烈，見習督察約40人爭1個位，警員則10選1。翻查資料，即使是預科畢業者，<span style=\"color: red;\">督察起薪點已為42,665元；假如手持學位或同等學歷，起薪點為43,980元，高級督察頂薪更高達84,250元</span>。"},{"pid":"d2ebb36ab113bde7e45ee7898cf51242249011fa","tid":2001811,"uid":300782,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T21:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59af619caa8aed72c66959b4bba424f0e90e7427","tid":2001811,"uid":50386,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T21:35:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190407/20650717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190407%2F20650717&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1ns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=dd5d4947\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190407%2F20650717&h=a4f9105f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190407/20650717</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">20190407<br />\n此post已完</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc6cf0a43b4cc69d9f209b487b73c497bea6bcaa","tid":2001811,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike"